This comes on behalf of a dedicated customer:

As described in [this KB|https://confluence.atlassian.com/display/GHKB/Story+Points+Not+Shown+in+the+Sprint+Report], if you edit an issue in a sprint after starting the sprint, you do not see the change in its story points in the Sprint Report but only in the Burndown Chart. This seems like expected behavior but, on behalf of our customer, could we verify this, please?

